description: Tamas Szekeres's legendary GDAL and GDAL.Native nugets repackaged with GDAL 2.4 from GISInternals, includes all required binaries. GDAL is a translator library for raster geospatial data formats that is released under an X/MIT style Open Source license by the Open Source Geospatial Foundation. As a library, it presents a single abstract data model to the calling application for all supported formats.
